headline.main: Mosul Train Tunnel Reveals Assault Course for Elite Islamic State Fighters
headline.print_headline: Mosul Train Tunnel Reveals Assault Course for Elite Islamic State Fighters

lead_paragraph: The mouth of the tunnel is hardly visible on a muddy hillside overlooking Mosul, where fighting now rages between Iraqi forces and Islamic State militants.
